import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { UIStore } from "./UIStore"
import { Playground, PropsTable } from "docz"

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"ui-store"}}>{`UI Store`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"store"}}>{`Store`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"message-bars-forms"}}>{`Message Bars, Forms`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
